USING THE LIBRARY
Just include a .hh file.
=========================================================================
GENERATING THE HTML DOCUMENTATION WITH DOXYGEN
In the directory geocomp:
mkdir doc
doxygen doc-config-file
=========================================================================
GENERATING THE EXAMPLE
- CImg examples (need to install CImg)
  In the directory geocomp run the script install.
